+note right of EMRSystem
+  ACID workflows: admission → encounter → orders → billing → claims execute within a shared transactionId; commit/rollback with audit trail and configurable isolation to prevent partial writes.
+end note
+
+note "3NF assured: every class has a single key (UUID/code/id) and only atomic attributes; no transitive dependencies between patient, clinical, and financial data." as N3NF
+N3NF .. PatientRecord
+
+note "Optimistic locking via version prevents ghost writes on Inpatient, Outpatient, EmergencyCase, LabResult, RadiologyImage, InsuranceClaim, BillingInvoice." as NLock
+NLock .. Inpatient
+NLock .. Outpatient
+NLock .. EmergencyCase
+NLock .. LabResult
+NLock .. RadiologyImage
